@startuml state-event-lifecycle

skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam pageMargin 10

title Internal Domain Event Lifecycle

[*] --> Created : Domain operation\ncompletes

Created : EventId = NewGuid()
Created : CreatedAt = UtcNow

Created --> Dispatched : DomainEventDispatcher\n.DispatchAsync()

Dispatched : Routed to matching\nin-process handlers

Dispatched --> Handled : Handler executes\nside effects

Handled : Projections, audit,\nor dependent state updated

Handled --> [*]

Dispatched --> Failed : Handler throws\nor validation fails
Failed --> [*]

@enduml
